<div class="headline"><h1>Professional athletes appear to learn faster than university students</h1></div>
<h3 class="deck">Brain's ability to focus may be key to athletic prowess</h3>
<h5 class="byline">
By Emily Chung, 
<a href="/news/credit.html">CBC News</a>
</h5>

<h4 class="posted">Posted:

Feb  1, 2013   8:19 AM ET


</h4>

<h4 class="lastupdated">Last Updated: 

Feb  1, 2013   2:16 PM ET


</h4>
<span class="socialicons rec" title="2000559900">&nbsp;</span>


				</div>
